seo: 万户OA,任意文件下载漏洞,downloadhttp.jsp,漏洞检测,指纹识别
seo_en: Wanhu OA, arbitrary file download vulnerability, downloadhttp.jsp, vulnerability detection, fingerprint identification
summary: 该插件用于检测万户OA系统的downloadhttp.jsp文件是否存在任意文件下载漏洞，并通过指纹识别确认目标系统。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect whether the downloadhttp.jsp file in Wanhu OA system has arbitrary file download vulnerability and confirms the target system through fingerprint identification.
